{"tid":947060,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［遍地開花］捷克總理下令辦公室停用華為手機","createTime":"2018-12-19T03:46:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T03:47:15.000Z","uid":79382,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5b5704f46ee8bb1132249e33db1b915bbda6f43d","tid":947060,"uid":79382,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T03:46:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%85%a9%e5%b2%b8/article/20181219/s00004/1545190036606/%e6%8d%b7%e5%85%8b%e7%b8%bd%e7%90%86%e4%b8%8b%e4%bb%a4%e8%be%a6%e5%85%ac%e5%ae%a4%e5%81%9c%e7%94%a8%e8%8f%af%e7%82%ba%e6%89%8b%e6%a9%9f\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25b2%25b8%2Farticle%2F20181219%2Fs00004%2F1545190036606%2F%25e6%258d%25b7%25e5%2585%258b%25e7%25b8%25bd%25e7%2590%2586%25e4%25b8%258b%25e4%25bb%25a4%25e8%25be%25a6%25e5%2585%25ac%25e5%25ae%25a4%25e5%2581%259c%25e7%2594%25a8%25e8%258f%25af%25e7%2582%25ba%25e6%2589%258b%25e6%25a9%259f&d=pvhBAVBnmSzUoSw0xFwVY7%2BnoHux5cIPnxEj5ZZbdh4%3D&h=8161893d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25e5%2585%25a9%25e5%25b2%25b8%2Farticle%2F20181219%2Fs00004%2F1545190036606%2F%25e6%258d%25b7%25e5%2585%258b%25e7%25b8%25bd%25e7%2590%2586%25e4%25b8%258b%25e4%25bb%25a4%25e8%25be%25a6%25e5%2585%25ac%25e5%25ae%25a4%25e5%2581%259c%25e7%2594%25a8%25e8%258f%25af%25e7%2582%25ba%25e6%2589%258b%25e6%25a9%259f&h=1282f6c6\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/%e5%85%a9%e5%b2%b8/article/20181219/s00004/1545190036606/%e6%8d%b7%e5%85%8b%e7%b8%bd%e7%90%86%e4%b8%8b%e4%bb%a4%e8%be%a6%e5%85%ac%e5%ae%a4%e5%81%9c%e7%94%a8%e8%8f%af%e7%82%ba%e6%89%8b%e6%a9%9f</a><br />\n<br />\n捷克總理巴比什於當地時間周二（18日）下令，其政府辦公室禁止使用中國華為手機。捷克工業和貿易部表示會跟隨總理要求，而其他使用華為產品的政府部門可能會仿效。<br />\n<br />\n捷克國家網絡與信息安全局周一（17日）曾警告，華為和中興通訊製造的硬件和軟件構成安全威脅。華為否認指控。<br />\n<br />\n美國近月向其他國家施壓，要求限制使用華為的技術，因可能被監視及竊取信息。目前日本、澳洲及新西蘭等國響應。<br />\n<br />\n(美國廣播公司)"},{"pid":"c30e71e1536ba688e48015e3ff3017825b1ebd90","tid":947060,"uid":41423,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T03:47:15.000Z","msg":"好"}]}